                    <Style />
                  </TextRun>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>. </Value>
                    <Style />
                  </TextRun>
                </TextRuns>
                <Style />
              </Paragraph>
              <Paragraph>
                <TextRuns>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>The whole amount of the loan shall be used only for the purpose set out here in. The Sacco shall have the right to</Value>
                    <Style />
                  </TextRun>
                </TextRuns>
                <Style />
              </Paragraph>
              <Paragraph>
                <TextRuns>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>demand immediate payment of any amount of loan outstanding, together with interest, if it shall come to the notice
of the Sacco that the whole or any part of the loan has been or is being expended for any other purpose.</Value>
                    <Style />
                  </TextRun>
                </TextRuns>
                <Style />
              </Paragraph>
              <Paragraph>
                <TextRuns>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value xml:space="preserve">
</Value>
                    <Style />
                  </TextRun>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>LENDING RATE </Value>
                    <Style>
                      <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                    </Style>
                  </TextRun>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>The loan will be charged a rate of </Value>
                    <Style />
                  </TextRun>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>=First(Fields!Interest_Rate.Value, "DataSet_Result")</Value>
                    <Style>
                      <Format>n2</Format>
                    </Style>
                  </TextRun>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>% per Annum. Review of interest chargeable shall be subject
to prevailing economic environment. However the Sacco reserves the right to vary the rate of
interest at its sole discretion subject to compliance with any regulatory requirement at any time
without reference to you.</Value>
                    <Style />
                  </TextRun>
                </TextRuns>
                <Style />
              </Paragraph>
              <Paragraph>
                <TextRuns>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value xml:space="preserve">
</Value>
                    <Style />
                  </TextRun>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>DEFAULT INTEREST </Value>
                    <Style>
                      <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                    </Style>
                  </TextRun>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>In the event of any default, all facilities outstanding will become due and payable immediately.
The amount in arrears will attract default interest at 3% above the prevailing lending rate.</Value>
                    <Style />
                  </TextRun>
                </TextRuns>
                <Style />
              </Paragraph>
              <Paragraph>
                <TextRuns>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value xml:space="preserve">
</Value>
                    <Style />
                  </TextRun>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>INSTALLMENT DATE </Value>
                    <Style>
                      <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                    </Style>
                  </TextRun>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>The first installment shall fall due 30 days upon disbursement of the loan amount and the
monthly repayment falls due.</Value>
                    <Style />
