(c) Payment of 0% risk management fee/Refinance fee of 2% (one off) (Kshs. </Value>
                    <Style />
                  </TextRun>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>=First(Fields!Approved_Amount.Value, "DataSet_Result")</Value>
                    <Style />
                  </TextRun>
                  <TextRun>
